The '''Foran Tutha star probe''' was an ancient wrecked [[Starship/Legends|starship]] found on [[Foran Tutha/Legends|Foran Tutha]] around [[500 BBY/Legends|500 BBY]]. It is considered one of the greatest discoveries of the post-[[Ruusan Reformations/Legends|Ruusan Reformation]] era. Scholars were divided on its origins as [[Celestial/Legends|Celestial]], [[Rakata/Legends|Rakatan]], or early [[Core Worlds/Legends|Core]] technology.

